fields.name: X-Lite X-803 Ultra Carbon - Puro Sport Red
fields.description: X-lite's exclusive high-carbon version of the X-803. A full-face racing helmet for the most demanding of motorcyclists thanks to its compact size, double action visor, racing air flow ventilation system, and carbon fitting comfort lining.

fields.name: Spada Lycan - White
fields.description: Open-face helmet with anti-scratch long visor, internal sun visor, and integrated rear spoiler.

fields.name: Weise Victory Leather Gloves - Brown
fields.description: Goat leather construction, padded by memory foam inside the knuckles. Knuckle and finger reinforcement with a leather overlay with adjustable hook, loop wrist strap, and small rubber cuff grip.

fields.name: RST GT CE Leather Jacket - Black
fields.description:
Full grain drum-tanned cow leather construction with perforated leather zones for added airflow. 
3D bubble fixed mesh lining for enhanced comfort. CE level 2 shoulder, elbow armor, and back protector are CE certified to level 2. Full RST jacket to jeans connection zip.

fields.name: TCX Hero Waterproof Boots - Vintage Brown
fields.description: Full grain leather construction with waterproof lining and toe and heel counter. Leather shift pad and anatomic and replaceable footbed Lacing fastening system with zipping and velcro band closure. The sole tread offers a superior grip on any terrain.

fields.name: RST GT CE Leather Jeans - Black
fields.description: Full grain drum-tanned cow leather construction with perforated leather zones for added airflow. 3D bubble fixed mesh lining for enhanced comfort. CE level 2 knee and hip armor. Full RST jacket to jeans connection zip with velcro backed RST knee sliders.

fields.name: Caberg Freeride Indy - Matt Black
fields.description: The Freeride is the new Caberg jet with a stylish and vintage look, constructed using aramid and fibreglass. The small-sized shell is one of the smallest on the market enabling it to reach a weight slightly above 800 grams so that it can easily fit under narrow seats. The Freeride can be used either with a long clear visor included in the helmet box or with Caberg vintage goggles, available as a spare part.

fields.name: Caberg Uptown - Gloss White
fields.description: The Caberg Uptown jet helmet is a classic look useful for everyday urban routes. Featuring two front air vents along with rear extractors ensure perfect ventilation while the easy to use inner sun-visor allows adjustment for all light conditions. The outer transparent visor is anti-scratch treated and is Pinlock ready. A micrometric buckle retention system allows for safe and easy adjustments. The Caberg Uptown is also equipped with a ring to secure the helmet to the motorcycle and a removable, washable lining.

fields.name: Forma Adventure Low Boots - Brown
fields.description: The new Forma Adventure low combines the comfort and flexibility of a road boot with the features of an off-road boot. Perfect for adventure touring, and for riders with larger calves.

fields.name: Furygan TD12 Gloves - Black
fields.description: The TD12 is a summer glove offering brilliant ventilation to keep your hands dry, even on the hottest days, and although lightweight, it definitely does not neglect the required standards of protection for a motorcycle glove.

fields.name: Knox Orsa Leather Gloves MkII - Black
fields.description:
The Orsa leather glove MkII is a well-established and highly-rated perforated summer glove from the Knox range. It features a honeycomb gel over a floating knuckle area, backed with memory foam, which in turn is housed in a flexible but durable outer knuckle shell designed to absorb impact. The perforated goat skin upper has abrasion-resistant finger sliders on the top of the fingers. They also feature touchscreen technology on the index finger.

Superior comfort is delivered via wrap-round seamless finger ends. Meanwhile, the strong goat skin palm has a soft memory foam double layer on high-wear areas and also utilises the patented Knox Impact Scaphoid Protection System (SPS) on the palm, which incorporates Micro-Lock technology for added impact absorption. The SPS eliminates the grab effect that occurs when a leather palm makes contact with the road, reducing the risk of hyperextension, which can cause a broken scaphoid.
A unique low-profile BOA wrist closure system eliminates the need for any hook and loop closers. This 'dialled-in' micro-adjustable fit slips easily under a jacket sleeve.

fields.name: HJC HJC CS-15 - Trion Red
fields.description: The CS-15 features HJC's advanced channelling system to direct air around the skull for maximum cooling and a matching machine-washable removable comfort liner. The latest CAD-engineered internals guarantee the legendary HJC comfort fit and a quick-release anti-fog prepared visor provides good visibility regardless of the conditions. a micro-buckle retention strap completes this good-looking, user-friendly helmet.

fields.name: LS2 Bob Lines - Black
fields.description: The LS2 Bob helmet features a high-performance fibre composite construction. This carefully layered blend of unique weave fibres, pre-impregnated with resin, into a strong, ultra-lightweight but rigid shell, accepts an impact while dispersing energy for a safer ride.

fields.name: MT Le Mans 2 SV - Skull & Roses Black / Red
fields.description: Classic lines and shape, the Le Mans 2 SV helmet from MT offers a timeless design that still looks great today. The inclusion of a multi-density EPS ensures safety and comfort and reduces bulky side padding. A washable faux leather interior and micrometric buckle fastening add practicality.

fields.name: Nolan N87 N-Com - Classic Metal White
fields.description: Nolan's top of the range N87 full-face helmet is packed full of features making it a good solid choice. With its sporty presence and unique features such as a tilt visor mechanism, N-Com intercom ready, Eyewear Adaptive system and an integrated drop-down sun-visor. The Nolan N87 is ready for the road.

fields.name: Oxford Clothing Oxford Mondial Advanced Textile Jeans - Black
fields.description: The Mondial pants are created with a Laminate construction and help to keep the rider cool, dry and warm depending on the conditions. Designed to provide unrestricted movement in extreme riding conditions, using technical laminated fabrics to minimise weight whilst maximising protection against the elements.

fields.name: Oxford Continental Advanced Textile Jacket - Tech Grey
fields.description: The Oxford Continental is a highly versatile 3-layer jacket designed to be worn in all four seasons. Comprising of a highly ventilated outer shell with a detachable waterproof liner and removable thermal liner, meaning it can be used in hot, cold and wet weather conditions.

fields.name: Oxford Clothing Oxford Mondial Advanced Textile Jacket - Tech Black
fields.description: As they say, there is no such thing as bad weather, just bad gear. Today's riding jackets are expected to be technically brilliant but that comes at a price with laminate jackets appearing at the top of that pile. Enter the new Oxford Mondial - technically brilliant but at a price that is within reach of all discerning motorcycle riders. In addition, it's lightweight, doesn't hold water in a downpour and dries out really quickly.

fields.name: Oxford Original Approved Denim Jeans Slim Fit - 2 Year Aged
fields.description: What if regular jeans offered the same protection as heavy-duty riding pants? After continuous testing, both in the lab and out on the road, Oxford introduces Armourlite. Highly durable denim that maintains a vintage look and softness. Working with skilled weavers to include a polyamide fibre into the weave, a hard-wearing material originally developed by the military for parachute cords. Two-way stretch was added to enhance mobility and comfort, along with quick dry technology which draws sweat and increases water-repellent effects.

fields.name: Oxford Original Approved Denim Jeans Straight Fit - 2 Year Aged
fields.description: What if regular jeans offered the same protection as heavy-duty riding pants? After continuous testing, both in the lab and out on the road, Oxford introduces Armourlite. Highly durable denim that maintains a vintage look and softness. Working with skilled weavers to include a polyamide fibre into the weave, a hard-wearing material originally developed by the military for parachute cords. Two-way stretch was added to enhance mobility and comfort, along with quick dry technology which draws sweat and increases water-repellent effects

fields.name: Oxford Hardy Wax Textile Jacket - Olive
fields.description:
Micro mesh breathable wax cotton and polyester construction with removable quilted thermal liner.
CE armour at elbows and shoulders. Pocket for an optional back protector. Two front exterior chest pockets and two zipped hand pockets with dual ventilation for increased airflow. Reflective components for increased visibility. Popper-secured cuffs and collar closure system with removable Velcro badge patch.

fields.name: Premier Vintage - OP Rust / Patina
fields.description: Classic open-face vintage design with Dyneema aramid fibre and epoxy resin construction. Removable and washable sanitised interior plus easy to use internal drop-down sun visor. Quick-release micrometric chin strap with padded strap for enhanced comfort. Weighs approximately 990g (+/- 50g).

fields.name: Rev'it Eclipse Textile Jacket - Brown
fields.description: The Eclipse jacket brings it back to basics when it comes to riding in high temperatures. The impact zones are made of abrasion-resistant polyester 600D, while the front, back and inner arms are mesh to allow full airflow to the upper body. CE shoulder and elbow armour comes standard and is upgradable with an optional Seesoft CE level 2 back protector. Various adjustment straps allow the rider to create a close fit, and the jeans loops allow the Eclipse to be attached to Rev'it jeans.

fields.name: Richa Richa Atomic Textile Jacket - Grey
fields.description: Abrasion-resistant textile construction with an internal mesh liner for enhanced comfort. D3O protection on the shoulders, elbow and back. Waterproof 8000mm membrane. Detachable hoodie with a snap button system. Attained CE rating prEN 17092-4:2018 A.

fields.name: Richa Blade Waterproof Boots - Black / Red
fields.description: Synthetic leathertex construction with internal waterproof lining and stretch instep for enhanced walking comfort. Replaceable metal toe slider, protection at the shins, ankles and heels with zipping with hook and loop closure.

fields.name: Richa Slick Waterproof Boots - Black
fields.description: Leather suede outer construction with Hipora waterproof and breathable membrane. Night-time visible reflective side inserts. Hook and loop with a lace closure system and reinforced heel and toes with leather gear change pad.

fields.name: Richa Richa Carbon Winter Waterproof Leather Gloves - Black
fields.description: The Richa Carbon Winter are durable weatherproof gloves. Carbon-reinforced fingers enhance the practicality whilst not compromising on styling. Reinforced palm, suede visor wiper and comfort thermal lining enhance this glove's versatility.

fields.name: Richa Richa Daytona 2 Leather Jacket - Brown
fields.description: High-quality buffalo leather construction for durability. Retro shoulder stitching for added style with removable thermal liner ideal for colder rides. D3O back, elbow and shoulder armour. Short connection zip to attach to trousers with large front zip with snap button neck closure. Attained CE rating prEN 17092-3:2018 AA

fields.name: RST X Kevlar® Tech Pro CE Aramid Fibre Jeans - Black
fields.description: Casual-looking Cordura denim jeans with Aramid fibre-reinforced liner. Fixed mesh lining for comfort. CE level 2 hip and knee protection.

fields.name: RST GT CE Leather Jeans - Black / Black
fields.description: Full grain drum-tanned cow leather construction with perforated leather zones for added airflow. 3D bubble fixed mesh lining for enhanced comfort. CE level 2 knee and hip armour. Full RST jacket to jeans connection zip with velcro-backed RST knee sliders.

fields.name: RST RST Stunt 3 CE Mixed Gloves - Black
fields.description: An excellent combination with a textile jacket, the Stunt 3 is a mid-length, comfortable glove. The soft aniline palm and little finger are reinforced with extra leather, the fingers have soft PU vents and ventilated leather panels for warm weather comfort. Add to that a carbon knuckle and super-fabric side re-enforcement and the Stunt 3 offers everything you could want in a mid-length sports glove

fields.name: RST Brixton CE Textile Jacket - Black
fields.description: HD wax cotton outer shell construction with removable thermal quilted liner for cold rides and detachable comfort lining ideal for hot weather. Strong Max zips used for added durability with coates bonded nylon triple stitched seams and zipped chest vents for customisable airflow Hook and loop adjustable cuff and waist tabs. CE-certified shoulder and elbow armour with accommodation for a back protector insert.

fields.name: RST RST Rider CE Textile Gloves - Black
fields.description: The synthetic textile outer construction with abrasion-resistant reinforced palm. Soft memory foam knuckle armour with hook and loop wrist closure system.

fields.name: RST Tractech Evo 3 CE Waterproof Boots - Black / Black
fields.description: Waterproof and breathable membrane with abrasion-resistant microfibre construction and breathable membrane for added comfort. Strong TPU shin and heel protection and hinged ankle prevent overextension. Calf expansion panel for added flexibility. Hard-wearing gear shift protection pad with anti-slip multi-density sole for added grip. Nylon boot shank for enhanced durability and anti-twist mid sole for a sturdy finish. Zip closure with hook and loop flap with replaceable hard-wearing toe slider

fields.name: Shark D-Skwal 2 - Penxa Black / Green / Yellow
fields.description: Constructed from injected thermoplastic resin, Shark's D-Skwal 2 takes motorcycle helmet safety to the next level. Every D-Skwal 2 helmet features a Maxvision pinlock visor, integrated anti-scratch sun visor, and planned locations for Sharktooth, Shark's in-house developed Bluetooth communication system.

fields.name: Shark Shark Drak - Evok Black / Red
fields.description: A must-have streetfighter-style helmet packed full of features. The Shark Drak (previously known as the Shark Raw) is equipped with a protective face mask and removable anti-scratch and anti-fog treated goggles. The Shark Drak is Sharktooth ready and has washable natural fibre interiors and a full ventilation system to keep you cool on those hot days.

fields.name: Shark Ridill 1.2 - Blank White
fields.description:
Built on the same basis as the S700S featuring redesigned ventilation and a special channel to accommodate glasses. Pinlock ready quick release visor with quick release retention system.
Thermoplastic construction and Integrated interior sun visor. Removable and washable interior lining and 
easy fit system for glasses wearers. Weight 1550g (+/-50g)

fields.name: Shoei GT Air 2 - Black
fields.description: The Shoei GT Air II has the innovative and highly-acclaimed GT-Air as a baseline… the GT-Air II was destined for greatness from the very start. Advancements in design, functionality and performance have further evolved Shoei's premium full-face touring helmet, yielding even easier adaptation to the ever-changing conditions throughout your journeys. Featuring a lengthened internal sun visor for optimal sun-glare protection, an all-new "first position" visor opening for advanced ventilation and defogging, enhanced aerodynamics and noise-reduction technology, and the ability to seamlessly integrate with the Sena SRL2 Communication System, the GT-Air II is equipped it to accommodate your every need.

fields.name: Shoei J-O - Matt Black
fields.description: The Shoei J-O is a contemporary yet classic look helmet and is the result of design excellence combined with attention to detail in a small but feature packed open face helmet which is both good looking and practical. It features a compact multi-composite shell, various materials and careful design consideration of each component. The CJ-3 visor restricts the rolling-in of wind turbulence and also has a 3 point closure.

fields.name: Godzilla
fields.description: Bloody Godzilla mate!
